h</div> <span class="date">June 11th, 2009</span> <span class="time">3:01 am</span><p>Great article guys. I hadn&#8217;t heard of the Tick timetracker before, looks like a great app.</p><div class="commentmeta"><div class="reply"> <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='/2009/06/11/effective-strategy-to-estimate-time-for-your-design-projects/?replytocom=357240#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-357240", "357240", "respond", "7742")'>Reply</a></div></div></div></div></li><li class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1 clearfix "> <span class="commentnumber">6</span><div class="comment" id="comment-357241"><div class="commentrating clearfix"><div class="rateresult">0</div> <a class="ratebtn down_active" id="btn-357241-down" style="opacity:0.3;" title="Vote down! (0 votes)"></a> <a class="ratebtn up_active" id="btn-357241-up" style="opacity:0.3;" title="Vote up! (0 votes)"></a></div><div class="gravatar"> <img alt='' src="http://media.smashingmagazine.com/cdn_smash/wp-content/themes/default-autosvn-stable/images/gravatar_default.png" lowsrc='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/02530069659f9f25a2044497dc961412?s=38&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F0.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D38&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-38 photo' height='38' width='38' /></div><div class="comment-text"><div class="comment-author">ilz</div> <span class="date">June 11th, 2009</span> <span class="time">3:02 am</span><p>&#8220;The Daily Grind&#8221; is the name of a little widget for the mac dashboard for keeping track of time. Also, Freshbooks has a nice built in widget that connects right to your invoices.</p><div class="commentmeta"><div class="reply"> <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='/2009/06/11/effective-strategy-to-estimate-time-for-your-design-projects/?replytocom=357241#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-357241", "357241", "respond", "7742")'>Reply</a></div></div></div></div></li><li class="comment even t